mcp](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#mcp). #### [list](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#list-2). #### [auth](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#auth-1). #### [debug](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#debug). ### [models](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#models). ### [run](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#run-1). ### [session](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#session). #### [list](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#list-3). ### [stats](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#stats). ### [web](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#web). ### [plugin](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#plugin). #### [path](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#path). ### [debug](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#debug-1). ### [upgrade](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#upgrade). ### [Experimental](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#experimental).", "score": 0.7463059, "raw_content": "# CLI | OpenCode\n[Skip to content](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/#_top)\n\n[![Image 1](https://opencode.ai/docs/_astro/logo-dark.DOStV66V.svg)![Image 2](https://opencode.ai/docs/_astro/logo-light.B0yzR0O5.svg) OpenCode](https://opencode.ai/docs/)\n\n[app.header.home](https://opencode.ai/)[app.header.docs](https://opencode.ai/docs/)\n\n[](https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode)[](https://opencode.ai/discord)\n\nSearch Ctrl K\n\n Cancel \n\n*   [Intro](https://opencode.ai/docs/)\n*   [Config](https://opencode.ai/docs/config/)\n*   [Providers](https://opencode.ai/docs/providers/)\n*   [Network](https://opencode.ai/docs/network/)\n*   [Enterprise](https://opencode.ai/docs/enterprise/)\n*   [Troubleshooting](https://opencode.ai/docs/troubleshooting/)\n*   [Windows](https://opencode.ai/docs/windows-wsl)\n*   \nUsage \n    *   [Go](https://opencode.ai/docs/go/)\n    *   [TUI](https://opencode.ai/docs/tui/)\n    *   [CLI](https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/)\n    *   [Web](https://opencode.ai/docs/web/)\n    *   [IDE](https://opencode.ai/docs/ide/)\n    *   [Zen](https://opencode.ai/docs/zen/)\n    *   [Share](https://opencode.ai/docs/share/)\n    *   [GitHub](https://opencode.ai/docs/github/